ZGAI LAW FIRM MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
Version: 3.0.0-dev
Baseline Date: 2026-07-22
Status: Controlled LAN Trial

Backend: Spring Boot 2.7.18 (Java 11)
Frontend: Vue 3 + Element Plus + Vite
Database: H2 (Dev) / PostgreSQL 16 (Target)

Core Scope:
- Case and Client Management
- Filing Approval
- Case Files and NAS
- Invoice Application
- Knowledge Base and RAG Foundation

Deployment:
- Frontend: http://localhost:3017
- Backend: http://localhost:8080/api
- Accounts: initialized through environment variables or imported employee data

Documentation:
- PRD: PRD.md
- Handoff: handoff.md
- Readme: README.md
